HEADWORD: intervolution
<hw>in`ter*vo*lu"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
being intervolved or coiled up; a convolution; <as>as, the
<ex>intervolutions</ex> of a snake</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Hawthorne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
